  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p> <img src="/media/13093695/tignes-chairlift-wc-02-01-23-838x400.jpg" alt="April ski holidays" data-udi="umb://media/386df7fcf7b448ce8dc1e87dba232616" /></p>
<p>Make the most of March - If you are wondering where to go skiing or snowboarding in March, you are not alone, Inghams offer fantastic European &amp; Canadian resorts in high altitude destinations, meaning we can offer snow-sure winter holidays all the way through the season, including March.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" class="c-btn">View ski holiday deals</a></p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Best ski resorts in March</h2>
<p>When looking for the right resorts for your ski and snowboarding trips in March, you want to take a trip to the high altitude, glacier covered and snow-sure destinations.</p>
<div id="top" class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt"><span>Zermatt, Switzerland</span></a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13064605/switzerland_zermatt_couples-playing-snow.jpg" alt="zermattswis" data-udi="umb://media/701057486a5b49ef85bbf05f358b40a6" /></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/switzerland/zermatt">Zermatt</a> offers an impressive high altitude of 3,820m, making it a top destination for decent March snow conditions. </li>
<li>This resort is ideal for families and beginners due to Zermatt's abundant easy / blue runs, meaning lots of practice space for all ages and abilities. </li>
<li>This resort is car free, with electric carts and horse-drawn carriage, offering plenty of boutique restaurants and shops.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt" class="c-btn">View Zermatt</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens, France</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092574/val-thoren-skiier-408x200.jpg" alt="valthorens" data-udi="umb://media/e0b7d2d38b784de89cd1bebe3140fcb2" /></p>
<ul>
<li>With a high altitude of 3,200m, Val Thorens provides snowy pistes well into March and beyond.</li>
<li>The resort of <a href="/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/france/three-valleys-ski-area/val-thorens">Val Thorens </a>is ideal if you are looking for some fun Apres Ski, with plenty of pubs, bars and nightclubs.</li>
<li>With almost door-step skiing and lots of sunshine, especially in March, this lively village has a lot to offer with a relaxing evening atmosphere, offering plenty of restaurants and bars to chose from. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens" class="c-btn">View Val Thorens</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff">Banff, Canada</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13064980/skier-in-canada.jpg" alt="banffcanada" data-udi="umb://media/24e64c396c12401486ade96da4578e47" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A high altitude of 2,730m, Banff is certainly worth considering for some March skiing and is also a Canadian National Park so if full of natural beauty and surrounding nature. </li>
<li>Part of the Ski Big 3 area, Banff is a great for space if you are part of a group looking for a vast expanse of snow.</li>
<li><a href="/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/canada/banff">Banff</a> offers a warm welcome, with many cafes, bakeries and coffee shops as well as many other activities from skiing, such as snowshoeing or sledding.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff" class="c-btn">View Banff</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia"><span>Cervinia, Italy</span></a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13048645/cervinia.jpg" alt="cerviniaitaly" data-udi="umb://media/34090ed9f60e4ed1ad77a28601d26759" /></p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a> is one of the slightly lower of altitude of just over 2000m but the great thing is it's access - slopes connecting to Zermatt, nearby glaciers and a great lift system to accommodate. </li>
<li>With your international ski pass, the options are endless from this resort with extensive ski and snowboarding. The impressive network of ski slopes will easily keep you busy for a week and more.</li>
<li>Being on the Italian side, you can enjoy the best quality local Italian cuisine and après bars throughout this this resort. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia" class="c-btn">View Cervinia</a></p>
</div>
</div>
