<h2>Best apartments, hotels and chalets for March skiing</h2>
<p>Discover the best accommodation options in our March-time skiing resorts across Europe. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7}" title="Fairmont Banff Springs">Fairmont Springs</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13057817/france_three-valleys-ski-area_val-thorens_hotel_altapura_lobby_fire.jpg" alt="hotelfairmont" data-udi="umb://media/3d0cbbfc8d8b4dc98705e670f9238bfd" /></p>
<ul>
<li>If you are looking for opulence and luxury, then there is no better place to stay then whilst in Banff, Canada then at the Fairmont Banff Springs Hotel - a 5 star stay. With a castle-like appearance, fine dining in this resort's top restaurants and a relaxing spa that offers only sanctuary - this hotel will ensure your ski holiday is unrivalled.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada" class="c-btn">View Canada</a></span></span></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/675df3581eae4fccb83a8d8946dc7b10" href="/{localLink:umb://document/675df3581eae4fccb83a8d8946dc7b10}" title="Hotel Altapura">Hotel Altapura</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13057832/france_three-valleys-ski-area_val-thorens_hotel_altapura_sun_loungers.jpg" alt="hotelaltapura" data-udi="umb://media/2c2ee000868a4d2ab213ee6632bf7b51" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span></span>Well known as the 'highest ski palace' in Val Thorens, France, this iconic hotel certainly lives up to that name. With a modern take on mountain life, this hotel offers glamour, yet a homely atmosphere, with stunning views of its hillside surroundings. With ski-in ski-out and a sun terrace, indoors meets outdoors perfectly here.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France" class="c-btn">View France</a></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3c4313d7f57d40e7913caa6f34eb7e97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3c4313d7f57d40e7913caa6f34eb7e97}" title="Hotel Schonegg">Hotel Schonegg</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13067004/zermatt-night-view.jpg" alt="hotelschonegg" data-udi="umb://media/ec71ab60b1c9407091be05b4ff72acdf" /></p>
<ul>
<li>This beautiful, traditional hotel in Zermatt, Switzerland is a truly special and traditionally Swiss hotel (so much so, it was used in BBC1 drama The Night Manager). The atmospheric hotel offers panoramic views from its terrace and award winning restaurant. Not to mention its wellness spa with a Turkish bath which is certainly a  highlight.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View Switzerland</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div></div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ca8d71f3f36b4ecf8ea2907d22425def" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ca8d71f3f36b4ecf8ea2907d22425def}" title="Grand Hotel Cervino">Grand Cervino</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13086958/grand-hotel-cervino-metterhorn-view.jpg" alt="grandcervino" data-udi="umb://media/e7192a650f714e928f531cddb1c88dda" /></p>
<ul>
<li>The 5 star Grand Hotel Cervino in Cervinia is a special place to stay. With views, fine dining, a wellness spa and even a private shuttle service - this is the perfect hotel to unwind and relax after making the most of the slopes all day. Close to amenities such as ski hire, ski schools and lifts, its in a good location. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens" class="c-btn">View Italy</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3f6199e3513f4195a64860f100c41474" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f6199e3513f4195a64860f100c41474}?accommodationNode=23569&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=ITCH&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=ITCH0107&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=B4&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=19/12/2022&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=" title="Chalet Obergurgl" data-anchor="?accommodationNode=23569&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=ITCH&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=ITCH0107&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=B4&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=19/12/2022&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=">Chalet Obergurgl</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13074709/chaletobergurgl-luxuryapartments-outside-1.jpg" alt="chaletobergurgl" data-udi="umb://media/d2512c0acd1f4b588d1ee8e62e1b3726" /></p>
<ul>
<li>This chalet in Obergurgl sits in one of the higher altitude resorts. Luxury, self-catering chalet with all the amenities of a hotel. It offers so much convivence - only 80m from the lifts, groceries delivered to your door, it's own wellness &amp; spa area and close proximity to many of the restaurants and bars. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria" class="c-btn">View Austria</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/dc0bf3735d9c4563884a59cd39690619" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dc0bf3735d9c4563884a59cd39690619}" title="Cristal de l'Alpe Apartments">Cristal Apartments</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13076255/cgh-le-cristal-de-lalpe-espace-récréatif-studio-bergoend-1.jpg" alt="cristalapartments" data-udi="umb://media/ee9479ff71c9451a97576a89042e7f39" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Centre based of the high altitude resort (3,330m) of <strong>Alpe d'Huez </strong>are mountain themed and well decorated.  They boast extensive facilities from a large heated pool, fitness centre and on-site spa treatments. This well-equipped accommodation means each apartment has a balcony for the wonderful views. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France" class="c-btn">View France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>FAQ's for skiing holidays in March</h2>
<p><strong>Is there still snow in March?</strong>- Yes in some resorts. Our experts hand pick high altitude resorts so you can find a variety of destinations still under a blanket of snow in March. </p>
<p><strong>Can you ski anywhere in March? - </strong>Though there are still plenty of resorts open at this time time of year, you may find some of the resorts (usually the lower altitude ones) closed or with limited offerings. It is best to opt for a high altitude resort to get the best snow fall. </p>
<p><strong>What do I wear skiing in March?</strong>- It is slightly warmer in the mountains come March time, so you can certainly get away with slightly less layers or a lighter jacket. It is best to pack your usual items though just in case there is a day of heavy snowfall, making it feel colder.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3>When to go - <a data-udi="umb://document/fbe98b0631fa4ed388a302e2fd6d0a58" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fbe98b0631fa4ed388a302e2fd6d0a58}" title="February skiing" data-anchor="#">February</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13066668/maiskogel_schneespass_family.jpg" alt="togofebruary" data-udi="umb://media/a18b8bb82e094e61be6c43b73ed4a8ef" /></p>
</div>
</div>
